question: How many immunizations are uncovered by the payer Humana?
answers:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?immunizationId) AS ?uncoveredImmunizationCount)
WHERE {
   ?payer a syn:Payer; rdfs:label 'Humana'.
   ?immunization a syn:Immunization; syn:payerId ?payerId.
   ?payerId = ?payer.
   FILTER NOT EXISTS {?coverage syn:immunizationId ?immunizationId.}
}
